OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fhospital with leukaemia    
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Italy's former prime minister Silvio   
OL,6, Berlusconi is being treated for a type 
OL,7, of chronic leukaemia, hospital doctors 
OL,8, in Milan have confirmed.               
OL,10,FHe was rushed to intensive care on     
OL,11,FWednesday with breathing problems and  
OL,12,Fdoctors said he was suffering from a   
OL,13,Frelated lung infection.                
OL,15,FA four-time prime minister and media   
OL,16,Fmogul, Mr Berlusconi, 86, still leads  
OL,17,Fhis party and is an elected senator.   
OL,19,FBut he has had repeated health problems
OL,20,Fsince he contracted Covid-19 in 2020.  
